public class MySpawnRequestingClient
extends AgentSpawnClientNode

Press enter and this thing will request loading vivae with selected map. To run this demo: -Run the ROS core, e.g.: cd jroscore && ./jroscore -RUn the class SimulatorServer, e.g.: ./run vivae.ros.simulator.server.SimulatorServer -Run this class: ./run vivae.ros.simulator.client.demo.agent.MySpawnRequestingClient ..and press enter
